	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_ARSENAL_SHIP">
			<Text>Arsenal Ship</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_ARSENAL_SHIP_TEXT">
			<Text>An arsenal ship is a concept for a floating missile platform intended to have as many as fifteen vertical launch bays for mid-sized missiles, most likely cruise missiles. In some naval doctrines, arsenal ships would be commanded remotely by another ship, although as computer systems became more sophisticated some were converted to become largely autonomous.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_ARSENAL_SHIP_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Arsenal Ship is a futuristic companion to the Missile Cruiser. It can carry 15 Missile units, but only has a limited ranged attack, as well as air defenses.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_ARSENAL_SHIP_HELP">
			<Text>The Arsenal Ship is a futuristic companion to the Missile Cruiser. It can carry 15 Missile units, but only has a limited ranged attack, as well as air defenses. Available on the discovery of Advanced Ballistics. Requires [ICON_RES_OIL] Oil.</Text>
		</Row>		
	</Language_en_US>



